divs: Sighting Detailsi was out walking my dog at night, it was a clear sky so i was looking up at the stars then something caught my eye. it was atleest 4 lights all traveling at the same speed witch was way faster then an a airplane. i live in heavaly populated area so i see planes almost daily. the lights seemed to be one object and i think there was some distortion around it witch made me wonder if i realy had seen it. the speed of this object more closely resembles a shooting star, from the time i saw it i had enough time to think about taking a picture with my smart phone and then it was gone
